jops.protocol
Class JopsProtocol

java.lang.Object
  jops.protocol.JopsProtocol

public class JopsProtocol
extends java.lang.Object

Implementor of the JOPS client-server protocol. Note that the JOPS protocol is completely different from the BAPS protocol - one of the reasons why this project is more of a proof of concept than an actual replacement prototype.

Author:
Matt Windsor
